Packages 
Package Description
com.gsma.mobileconnect.cache
Interface for a cache that is used by the Mobile Connect Discovery SDK IDiscovery.
com.gsma.mobileconnect.discovery
Interface to the Mobile Connect Discovery SDK.
com.gsma.mobileconnect.helpers
These are non essential classes for mobile connect that provide an example usage of the Mobile Connect SDK.
com.gsma.mobileconnect.impl
Contains implementations of IDiscovery and IOIDC also a factory class to create instances Factory.
com.gsma.mobileconnect.oidc
Interface for the Mobile Connect OpenID Connect SDK.
com.gsma.mobileconnect.utils
Utility classes used by the Mobile Connect Discovery and OpenID Connect SDKs.

Mobile Connect Discovery and OpenID Connect SDK

This package provides a java SDK to Mobile Connect.

The main SDK interfaces are IDiscovery and IOIDC.
